{
  "id": "656550d4374759001c7a83f0",
  "title": "認知的な苦労の大きい目標",
  "created": 1701138646,
  "updated": 1707445865,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "656550d4374759001c7a83f0",
      "text": "認知的な苦労の大きい目標",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1701138646,
      "updated": 1701138733
    },
    {
      "id": "65c5784f1280f0000078e334",
      "text": "> [ultraviolet(@raurublock) https://twitter.com/raurublock/status/1729291605147087098]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707440206,
      "updated": 1707440209
    },
    {
      "id": "65c578521280f0000078e335",
      "text": "> [New study sheds light on ADHD's impact on motivation and the efficacy of amphetamine-based meds https://www.psypost.org/2023/11/new-study-sheds-light-on-adhds-impact-on-motivation-and-the-efficacy-of-amphetamine-based-meds-214742]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707440209,
      "updated": 1707440232
    },
    {
      "id": "65c578591280f0000078e338",
      "text": "> [ADHD]については、[アテンション]が逸れがちなことや[多動]、[衝動的行動]が注目されがちだが、どうも実はその背後に[動機付け]、特に「認知的な苦労の大きい目標への動機付け」が下がりやすいという高次の原因があるっぽく、[アンフェタミン]の投与がそれを劇的に改善する、という報告",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707440217,
      "updated": 1707440217
    },
    {
      "id": "656550f8aff09e0000a1c73f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1701138680,
      "updated": 1701138680
    },
    {
      "id": "656550d6aff09e0000a1c70c",
      "text": ">[raurublock https://twitter.com/raurublock/status/1729311326852551117] このADHDの人の動機付けの低下は、「[認知的な苦労が大きいが肉体的には楽なタスク]」で最も大きかったそうな。",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1701138646,
      "updated": 1707440269
    },
    {
      "id": "656550d6aff09e0000a1c70d",
      "text": "> ふと思ったんだが、ADHDが近年問題視されるようになった背景に、現代社会では日常生活や仕事におけるタスクがそういう「[認知的苦労]大＆肉体的に楽」なものばかりになってきたことが…",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1701138646,
      "updated": 1707440253
    },
    {
      "id": "656559d6b8bbfc0000559468",
      "text": "\t説得力ある[はるひ.icon][Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1701140951,
      "updated": 1701162133
    },
    {
      "id": "65674827e5172d0000956626",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1701267496,
      "updated": 1701267496
    },
    {
      "id": "65674828e5172d0000956627",
      "text": "[曖昧で大きな問題]だ[yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1701267496,
      "updated": 1701267506
    },
    {
      "id": "6567486ee5172d0000956628",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1701267566,
      "updated": 1701267566
    },
    {
      "id": "6567486ee5172d0000956629",
      "text": "肉体的には楽な方が動機づけの低下が大きいのはなぜだろう[yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1701267566,
      "updated": 1701267593
    },
    {
      "id": "656748d5e5172d000095662a",
      "text": " [作業興奮]的なものが起こりにくい？",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1701267669,
      "updated": 1701267684
    },
    {
      "id": "656748f2e5172d000095662b",
      "text": " 認知的な負荷も肉体的な負荷も大きいタスクってどんなのだろう",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1701267698,
      "updated": 1701267758
    },
    {
      "id": "65c58e5d79d3a900006b8733",
      "text": " \t対戦系のアスリートくらいしか思いつかない[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1707445854,
      "updated": 1707445865
    },
    {
      "id": "656550d6aff09e0000a1c70e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1701138646,
      "updated": 1701138646
    },
    {
      "id": "656550d8aff09e0000a1c722",
      "text": "逆に ADHD サバイバルガイド的なものは[認知負荷]が高い仕事に取り組む際の参考になる？[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1701138649,
      "updated": 1707440305
    },
    {
      "id": "65c578ab1280f0000078e339",
